# Fast Food Restaurant – 3D Environment

This project is a 3D environment of a modern fast-food restaurant created using Blender.

## Project Overview
The scene represents a stylish fast-food restaurant with rooftop seating and outdoor counters.  
The goal of this project was to practice environment design, hard-surface modeling, and scene composition.

## Features
- Modern fast-food restaurant design
- Rooftop dining area
- Outdoor serving counter
- Simple environment layout
- Clean modeling structure

## Software Used
- Blender

